instruction.level1: Schedule a code review meeting for the Python meetup on May 20th at 3 PM
instruction.level2: Create an event titled "Code Review Meeting for Python Meetup" on May 20th at 3 PM.
instruction.level3: Create an event titled 'Code Review Meeting for Python Meetup' on May 20th, 2026 at 3 PM

steps: Click the 'Create' button to start creating a new event
Click 'Event' from the menu to start creating a new calendar event.
Fill in the event title with 'Code Review Meeting for Python Meetup'
Fill in the event date with 'May 20, 2025'
Fill in the event date with 'Monday, May 20'
Fill in the event start time with '3:00 PM'
Click the 'Save' button to finalize creating the event.
